{"tid":1630294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要］抗爭要長期維持落去一定要放棄打陣地戰，轉為開花","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:09.000Z","uid":44160,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5635ef38015683198023d812cd7c8277e196a8a9","tid":1630294,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"經過今日，就見到陣地戰令到大量手足被捕，反而前兩日就冇事，可見開花嘅成功！<br />\n以後日頭遊行就比番和理非主導，勇武忍忍手，留番夜晚先各區開花！<br />\n我地真係唔可以再失去勇武手足架啦，難聽啲講句，一個勇武頂十個和理非！勇武巴真係唔好送頭呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"683078ab70c82e27e99f6026f3d2c46b55a4930e","tid":1630294,"uid":130079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:16.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a6c1871aa8440c7555f12008dcdba5def0070e47","tid":1630294,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"「戰略」搏一個星期，我地可以贏一世<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630040</a>"},{"pid":"38b5feca7d074c1522071bc396c357184e901d83","tid":1630294,"uid":303304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:07:38.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：文宣洗地開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5057002db563a67e017d523631e45ac779b7d019","tid":1630294,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d9ff62bbe2b4c36137f5b02e21f8e5fcf4ea29b","tid":1630294,"uid":44160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f714e149c6fbe220d3655670123c091ebfa986a8","tid":1630294,"uid":80528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"推 咪撚再預告係邊到遊行"},{"pid":"49fab9c047e519eb6b9dec13f1e3c86adeb835cd","tid":1630294,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:21:09.000Z","msg":"勇武真係忍忍手<br />\n唔FG出 唔代表和勇分離"}]}